DESCRIPTION:Join us on Wednesday\, October 22\, from 4–7 PM at Whispering Vine South Creek for an elegant tasting featuring the celebrated Far Niente family of wines\, including selections from Post & Beam\, Bella Union\, and Nickel & Nickel. Experience the craftsmanship and sophistication that have made Far Niente one of Napa Valley’s most enduring icons.\nTasting Fee: $35 (Buy a bottle from the tasting and your fee is refunded)\nFeatured Wines:\n• Post & Beam by Far Niente Cabernet Sauvignon 2022 – 95 pts Tasting Panel\, 92 pts Wine Enthusiast – Plush and refined with dark plum\, espresso\, and chocolate layered over satin-smooth tannins.\n• Post & Beam by Far Niente Carneros Chardonnay 2022 – 94 pts Wine Enthusiast\, 91 pts James Suckling – Rich and creamy with baked pear\, golden apple\, and toasted vanilla balanced by bright acidity.\n• Bella Union by Far Niente Cabernet Sauvignon 2022 – 95 pts Tasting Panel\, 92 pts Wine Enthusiast – Deep and expressive with cassis\, black cherry\, and dark chocolate unfolding through a long\, structured finish.\n• Nickel & Nickel Truchard Vineyard Chardonnay 2023 – 94 pts James Suckling\, 90 pts Wine Spectator – Elegant and vibrant with tangerine\, pear\, and honeysuckle over a mineral-driven\, polished finish.\nDiscover the artistry of the Far Niente portfolio\, where tradition\, precision\, and Napa Valley terroir unite in every glass.
LOCATION:85 Foothill Rd Ste 1 Reno\, NV 89511
